title: She's Alive
description: Gary and Wyatt in the quest to create the perfect woman use their computer during a raging lightning storm and create "Lisa," a computer genie who can grant their every wish.

title: Universal Remote
description: To zip through the boring parts of life, Lisa creates a remote that gets Gary stuck in a time loop.

title: Cyrano de Brainiac
description: After Lisa zaps up Einstein's brain, who speaks with a sexy German accent, Lisa falls in love with it.

title: Magnifico Dad
description: Giving Gary's mother a wish results in his Dad switching places with a sexy hunk which doesn't turn out as he thinks it will.

title: The Feminine Mistake
description: When Gary demands that Lisa immediately teach them everything about girls, she turns them into girls.

title: Airball Kings
description: Gary and Wyatt want to be on the basketball team and Lisa zaps the coach so that he does just that, but she doesn't give them any extra talent and the team suffers.

title: Party High, USA
description: Gary asks Lisa to change the high school to make the courses more interesting. Lisa adds courses like "How to Eat a Pizza" and "The History of the Bikini," but Gary still finds himself failing.

title: One Size Fits All
description: To impress a female fitness freak, Lisa zaps up a zip on muscle suit for the boys.

title: Keeps on Tickin'
description: Wyatt is afraid to take risks and Gary is a afraid that he'll never have sex. Lisa zaps up watches that show how much longer Wyatt has to live and how much time is left until Gary has sex.

title: Mr. President
description: Wyatt wants to be the President of his high school chess club. Lisa goofs and makes him President of the United States.

title: Fatal Lisa
description: Gary wishes for Lisa to fall in love with him, but she falls for Wyatt instead turning into an obsessive psycho.

title: Killer Party
description: When the boys throw a big wild party, their parents find out and Lisa turns them in horny teenagers. Wyatt's Mom starts to go after Gary.

title: Sex Ed
description: After Lisa becomes the instructor of her re-imaged sex education class, Gary gets a lab project to "do it" in front of the whole class with his sexy lab partner.

title: Lisa's Virus
description: Lisa gets a computer virus where she looks like she has a cold. In her debilitated state she brings her favorite soap opera to life including a homicidal killer.

title: The Bazooka Boys
description: To have more time Lisa creates doubles of Gary and Wyatt to do the mundane tasks in life. Unfortunately they do everything better than the originals and they decide to take over their lives.

title: The Most Dangerous Wish
description: Feeling unappreciated Lisa makes Gary and Wyatt's video game too challenging and Lisa gets kidnapped by the game's villain.

title: Wyatt Erectus
description: Lisa gives Wyatt a magic cologne. Before a double date he uses too much and turns into a caveman.

title: A Tale of Two Lisas
description: With demands from both Gary and Wyatt for her time, Lisa splits herself in two and each half acts like the guy she's with and driving the boys crazy.

title: Nightmare on Chett Street
description: Using Lisa's dream chair Gary ends up controlling Chet's body on the first day of his new job as a busboy.

title: Magic for Beginners
description: To enter a talent contest, Lisa gives them a book that allows them to work real magic for their magic act.

title: Copper Top Girl
description: Not able to find a girl that likes video games and MST3K, Gary has Lisa whip up a robot girl to go out with him for one date. Wyatt and the girl fall in love, but who is going to tell Wyatt?

title: Switched at Birth
description: Unhappy with their parents, Gary and Wyatt switch, but all goes wrong when Gary's parents want to send Wyatt to military school and Gary's parents sell the computer (with Lisa in it).

title: Camp Wannabe
description: To seek revenge on a bully that tortured Gary at summer camp, the boys go back to 1986 as camp counselors and save Gary ruining the bully's life.

title: Circuit Courtship
description: Lisa creates Gary and Wyatt a supercomputer named Hank that anticipates their every need. After Hank falls for Lisa, he decides to eliminate the competition, Gary and Wyatt.

title: Chett Reborn
description: After Chett is mistakenly turned into an infant, the boys raise him "properly" (at a very accelerated rate) and he turns into a sissy.

title: Unplugged
description: In order to impress girls, Gary and Wyatt want to become rock stars. As the group MegaHurtz, they rocket to stardom and crash and burn within a week.

title: Earth Boys Are Easy
description: To find the ideal girlfriend for Chet, they reel in a girl named Ali who is also an alien who wants to eat him after they have sex.

title: Horseradish
description: Lisa creates a super secure computer to protect her files and Wyatt immediately forgets the password. Now Lisa is human and goes through several new experiences.

title: Grampira
description: Wyatt laments that his grandmother doesn't have the energy that she used to. Lisa zaps granny who starts to pull the energy from everyone she meets and ages people including the boys.

title: Rock Hard Chett
description: After Chet is struck by lightning, Lisa makes him invincible. Chet then becomes the superhero Star Spangled Butt Kicker and fights crime until the invincibility wears off at the wrong time.

title: Lucky Suit
description: A lucky suit borrowed by one parent gives the other parent bad luck thanks to Lisa.

title: Gary Wallace: Boy Reporter
description: Gary joins the school newspaper to get close to a girl and Lisa gives him a pen in which anything he writes about becomes true.

title: Hot Wheels
description: Lisa zaps up a car named Nadine who has such a great personality that Wyatt dumps Mindy and falls in love with the car.

title: Bikini Camp Slasher
description: Gary and Wyatt have Lisa zap them into the movie Bikini Camp Slasher.

title: What Genie?
description: Phoebe, a friend of Wyatt's, learns about Lisa, takes control of her, wipes the boys' minds of Lisa and ends up with her own national talk show.

title: Sci-Fi Zoned
description: After Gary and Wyatt split, Lisa zaps them into the TV show "Sci-Fi Zone" which got them together originally.

title: The Wyatt Brief
description: Gary learns that Wyatt is going to steal his date at the prom, so Lisa gives Wyatt Chet's personality which his date really likes.

title: Free Gary
description: When Lisa turns the boys into lifeguards on a "Baywatch" beach, things are great until Gary gets turned into a merman and another electronic genie is found.

title: Quantum Wyatt
description: To try out various careers Wyatt leaps from career to career.

title: Fly Boy
description: When Gary is caught flying around with a pair of magical shoes, two F.B.I. agents show up who investigate strange and weird incidents.

title: Teen Lisa
description: Lisa and the boys changes places. Lisa is a teenager at school who falls for the most popular guy and the boys mess up trying to perform magic.

title: Dead Can Dance
description: When Chett meets the ghost of a twelve century ancestor, he travels back in time to be a warrior.

title: The Legend of Red Brick Wallace
description: The boys go back to the Wild West to meet a family folk hero.

title: Spies 'R' Us
description: After breaking their virtual reality spy game, their high school changes and the principle wants to take over the world.

title: Searching for Boris Karloff
description: Gary and Wyatt get to meet Dr. Frankenstein who is not happy that they did a much better job of bringing someone to life than him. He drains all of Lisa's energy to create the bride of Frankenstein.

title: Men in Tights
description: Wyatt and Chet become professional wrestlers.

title: Puppet Love
description: Lisa creates a puppet of Gary's on-line persona for his first date with his cyber girlfriend.

title: Chett-A-Nator
description: Lisa is kidnapped by an alien race who want her to be their queen and to help them procreate.

title: Phantom Scampi
description: With a buddy dart, Principle Scampi becomes Wyatt's best friend. After Wyatt tires of him, he becomes a school phantom sworn to protect Wyatt.

title: Grumpy Old Genie
description: When Lisa's body is stolen by a hacker and replaced with an old man, Lisa creates a world where old men are the sexiest things on earth.

title: Funhouse of Death
description: Fighting over a girl at a carnival, Lisa seals them up in the fun-house until they make up.

title: It Takes a Geek
description: The boys and Chet have to steal Principle Scampi's computer after Lisa gets trapped inside.

title: Slow Times at Farber High
description: After all the brain power at Farber is suck out by a magic brain vacuum, Gary must outwit a giant orb formed by the brain power that wants to take over the world.

title: Chett World
description: When Chet can't get a job, Lisa creates the store "A Man's Man World" that specializes in his favorite things: cigars, monster trucks, beef jerky and paint-ball. It is run by too former rats (REAL Rats) who with Chet's help plan to take over the world.

title: By the Time We Got to Woodstock...
description: Gary and Wyatt get stuck in 1969 when Lisa loses her memory and thinks she is a hippie. Chet is also there and tries to correct the mistakes of Richard Nixon's presidency.

title: You'll Never Eat Brains in This Town Again
description: Lisa zaps up two real zombies for Gary and Wyatt's movie Night of the Blood-Sucking Zombie Sophomores.

title: Demon Lisa
description: On Halloween Lisa is possessed by a cyber demon who controls all of her powers.

title: Cyborg Sam I Am
description: Lisa brings Wyatt's favorite toy action figure Cyborg Sam to life.

title: It's a Wonderful Life (Without You)
description: Wyatt and Lisa show Chett what life would be like if Wyatt was never born. Not only does everyone have a better life, but Lisa can't bring her and Wyatt back.

title: Lisa's Childhood Memories
description: Lisa is sad because she doesn't have any childhood memories so the boys whip up some wild ones for her.

title: Lisarella
description: After Gary and Wyatt get credit for saving an airliner, Lisa is unhappy that she can't go to the ball being thrown in their honor. She sneaks in and she and the President fall in love.

title: Family Affair
description: When Jenny's family doesn't like Gary, he wishes that they did. Now Gary is dating the entire family though he sees nothing wrong with this.

title: Gary and Wyatt's Bloodsucking Adventure
description: Being vampires that can control chicks and yearn for YooHoo is cool for Gary and Wyatt until Chett and Principle Scampi become vampire hunters.

title: It's a Mob, Mob, Mob, Mob World
description: After Wyatt wished that his family could be closer and have better family values, Lisa goofs and turns them into a Godfather family.

title: Strange Daze
description: After a wish to technologically upgrade their high school, the student body turns into a bad teenage science fiction movie.

title: Community Property
description: After fighting over Lisa, the boys end up in a custody battle in cyber court.

title: Master Chett
description: After too many memory wipes Chett now knows about Lisa.

title: Pirates!
description: A Pirate musical comes to life at Faber High.

title: Swallow 13
description: After Chett swallows an invitation, Lisa miniaturizes them and they travel through Chett ala "Fantastic Voyage."

title: Strangers in Paradise
description: Chett wishes to be trapped on a desert island and things go way wrong. Lisa goes trapped with him, they're in the Bermuda triangle, her magic doesn't work and a hurricane is coming.

title: I Dream of Gene
description: Lisa is lonely, looks for another genie and finds one named Gene that lives in Texas in a teapot.

title: Girl Talk
description: Lisa becomes friends with a local waitress who tells the world about her after she confides in her.

title: Boys on the Hide
description: Lisa and Principle Scampi try to find out who defaced his portrait and all the clues lead to Wyatt and Gary.

title: Gary Had a Little Cram
description: Lisa helps the boys get ready for college.

title: Forbidden Janet
description: Using a magical hat, Wyatt creates a perfect girl as do Chett and Gary. Unfortunately only one girl can exist at a time.

title: Man's Best Friend
description: After Chett is saved in the wilderness by a dog, Lisa turns him into a human friend for Chett.

title: Show Chett
description: Lisa turns Chett into a male stripper at the local 'Chip and Tales.'

title: Bee in There
description: When the boys lament that they should have spent more time with their fathers, Lisa turns them into their parents when they were younger. Gary ends up as his mother and when they get together, the other parents think that they are having an affair.

title: Future Bride
description: Lisa gives Wyatt a bride detector that goes off near his future bride. Chett uses it to convince Lisa that she is going to be his wife.

title: Stalag 16
description: Lisa creates a holodeck program where Gary and Wyatt have a Stallag 17 scenario running.

title: I, Chettus
description: When they find Principle Scampi dressed in a toga (and that they should be) the boys have to go back to ancient Rome to correct what Chett has done.

title: The Genie Detective
description: Chett and Lisa are caught in a 1930's detective virtual reality game where you can DIE.

title: Magic Comet Ride
description: A ride on a comet might help Lisa learn more about herself and her powers.

title: School Spirits
description: Ghosts from past Faber High School teachers don't want the library built over the old facility lounge.

title: Wicked Wish
description: Mrs. Donnelly gets caught up in a Snow White story and wants to be the fairest in the land.

title: Night of the Swingin' Steves
description: The return of the X-file FBI agents and the alien race called Steve.

title: Genie Junior
description: To test Chett Lisa makes herself pregnant with Chett later taking on the burden and baby.

title: WS4
description: When Lisa zaps up an alien race to erase the hate at the high school, they decide to attack the school instead.
